Buying Raw or PSA graded, using PayPal.

I also have a Spike Shannon T206 PSA 1 for trade! In return I am looking for either a Raw Dineen, or a PSA 1/Authentic Dineen!

Thanks for looking!

~Owen

NOTE: Will send scan of Shannon if requested. :D
